lead_paragraph: A federal judge on Thursday dismissed a lawsuit accusing Major League Baseball's 30 teams of conspiring not to poach each other's scouts and refusing to pay them overtime.

headline.print_headline: Judge Dismisses Scouts' Lawsuit Against Major League Baseball
headline.main: Judge Dismisses Scouts' Lawsuit Against Major League Baseball
